Package: python-buttonshim
Architecture: all
Section: python
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, python-smbus
Suggests: python-psutil, python-requests
Description: Python library for the Pimoroni Button SHIM
 Button SHIM provides one super-bright RGB LED indicator and 5 buttons.
 Ideal for adding input to your Raspberry Pi project.
 .
 This is the Python 2 version of the package.

